assets.description:
Here is my futuristic car design (https://3dhaupt.com/futuristic-car-game-ready-download/) . 

I modeled, textured and rigged this car in Blender (https://www.blender.org/). 

The concept was created by Piotr Kupsc (https://goo.gl/GtVuRb).


Here are some cool projects where this car has found a use:

Futuristic Car painting contest (https://goo.gl/d0o32l)

Kosmiczny Kowboj - Cyberpunkish city street (https://goo.gl/L7IaHh)

First test for a racing game (https://goo.gl/K5Gvd8) by rocco martino

Short movie celflux (https://goo.gl/ibKeK7) by GemGfx (https://goo.gl/9cuXbe)

Test in Arma3 (https://goo.gl/7XHqWO) by ThrompTOH
